pageContext.quote: And then you realize that this area of stuff that you don’t know is almost infinite. So, you realize that learning in programming — it cannotbe completed. Not even close. You just have to pick like, a path inside ofit and go slowly and just grow and compare yourself to the person that youwere yesterday. That feeling of, “Oh my god, there is so much that I don’tknow,” that feeling will not go away by learning more. It will grow - to apoint where you just realize, “Oh...uh...OK.”
